Body: Description: Transaction (Process ID 86) was deadlocked on lock resources with another process and has been chosen as the deadlock victim. Rerun the transaction. The collection job returned error and subsequent reports generated were not having correct data.

What We've Learned Updated: Customer has a customer "SHELL_ALLUserAccount" activity scan job that is failing with this error:

Next Steps Updated: Support asked customer to provide additional details and collect debug logs.
